  <description type="morphology">Stems 2–3 cm, dark green or yellowish brown, branches straight. Leaves erect or slightly homomallous, 0.5–1 mm; margins erect, entire; apex abruptly short-acuminate or subulate; alar cells quadrate, walls thick, region extending 1/3 leaf margin; distal laminal cells 15–25 × 3–5 µm, walls thick. Seta yellow-orange, red, or purple, 0.5–1.5 cm. Capsule yellow to reddish brown, 0.9–1.5 mm. Spores 11–12 µm, smooth to minutely papillose.</description>
